{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"03fed02337","title":"坚决阻敌第一旅占领盐池","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e51ae1552c","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"03fed02337"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7cf83f85ce","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决阻敌第一旅占领盐池”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"496e1a3c0e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月22日）彭，并告宋、宋，谢、甘P：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"a45587181e","type":"paragraph","text":"胡令四十三师向萌城、甜水堡增援，而第一旅昨日已至青山街，离盐池不远。二十八军及骑兵团全部应立即转至青山街，小部由正面，主力由侧后，坚决阻止第一旅，不使盐池落入敌手，以待主力之到达。谢甘所部除小部警戒安边外，主力应立即集结盐池守城。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"9f57dcf77b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"b6b2894f2e","type":"paragraph","text":"二十二日十七时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"b89e5e3cd4","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军前敌总指挥兼政治委员、第一方面军司令员彭德怀等的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"e94250d9f1","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]宋、宋，指宋时轮、宋任穷，当时分别任红军第一方面军第二十八军军长和政治委员。谢、甘，指谢、甘渭汉，当时分别任红军第一方面军第二十九军军长和政治委员。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"},{"id":"53108adc50","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队司令兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337"}],"page":{"id":"c84efcf3cf","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"03fed02337","start":13,"end":13}}}},"__N_SSG":true}